1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:10,040
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,520
[Episode 4]

3
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:20,000
I'm just joking with you, young lady.

4
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,360
Was it fun?

5
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,880
Get up.

6
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,040
Let go of Lu Ping.

7
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,640
Why should I?

8
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,520
I've been wanting to capture him.

9
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,520
How foolish.

10
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,480
If Lu Ping is really from Shanhai Gang,

11
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,810
could he avoid Xing Luo?

12
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,800
Would he risk his life to save you?

13
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,560
I guess

14
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:05,800
he saved me so he can use me
to get near to Mr. Wen.

15
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,800
If he's not related to Shanhai Gang,

16
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,730
how does he know Xing Luo that well?

17
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,040
That day at the fort,

18
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:13,520
why do you want
to snatch the Shanhai Badge?

19
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,800
So, you're not talking.

20
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,279
After I escort you back,

21
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,000
I have a hundred ways to make you talk.

22
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,399
Can you be reasonable?

23
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,840
Su Tang.

24
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,640
This place isn't safe.

25
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,970
Go back to Zhaifeng Institute.

26
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,520
Furthermore,

27
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,000
Ms. Qin wants

28
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,400
to invite me to her house.

29
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:35,480
Her family is famous and highly respected.

30
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,010
She'll keep me safe.

31
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,360
Let's go.

32
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,720
Act according to the situation.

33
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:51,000
[Lu Ping's identity can't be exposed.]

34
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,840
[I must save him as soon as possible.]

35
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:55,720
[Ruyu Restaurant]

36
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:56,880
Mr. Wei.

37
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,080
You can't do so.

38
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:00,260
If you do so, Ms. Qin won't agree to it.

39
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,320
Bring Ms. Ling away

40
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,760
and treat her well.

41
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,160
Be gentle.

42
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,040
Let's go.

43
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,000
What's happening?

44
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,240
Mr. Wei.

45
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,610
Do you want me to act with you again?

46
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,080
This is a strategy

47
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:17,360
I devised specifically for Sangsang.

48
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,760
Beauties love heroes.

49
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,890
It's the truth for many centuries.

50
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,360
I employed these strong men

51
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,920
to cause trouble here.

52
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,160
Madam Jin, don't worry.

53
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:30,600
I'll pay you double
for all the damaged items.

54
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,360
I'll go prepare now.

55
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,300
You can start it later.

56
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:40,280
I'll come in time to stop it.

57
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,840
Please remember.

58
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:42,720
Be fierce.

59
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,000
The fiercer you are, the better.

60
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,120
This way, I can show

61
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,730
my bravery and mightiness.

62
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:50,120
Only then, Sangsang will remember me

63
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,280
and be impressed.

64
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,960
Mr. Wei, have a nice day.

65
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,130
Did you hear him?

66
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:59,010
He's paying double
for all the damaged items.

67
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,520
Ms. Qin.

68
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,960
Ms. Qin.

69
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,520
Wen Gecheng is indeed

70
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,760
my third maternal uncle's
grandpa's brother.

71
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,120
I'm alone now.

72
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,680
I want to go to him for shelter,

73
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,960
but I can't reach him.

74
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:19,320
I could only find you.

75
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,060
I can't do this.

76
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,400
I can't walk anymore.

77
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,880
Don't be such a baby.

78
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,080
If you don't walk,

79
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:26,560
I'll break your legs.

80
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,400
If you do so,

81
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:31,040
you'll have to carry me then.

82
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,840
I'm not being unreasonable.

83
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,050
I captured you because of the case.

84
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:43,050
Why does Shanhai Gang want to kill you?

85
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,580
If you can tell me the truth

86
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,560
or if you have any difficulties,

87
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,040
The Qins will protect you.

88
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,920
My life is in your hands.

89
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,650
Can I not tell you the truth?

90
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,640
Ms. Qin, take pity on me.

91
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,560
Tell me where Wen Gecheng is living.

92
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,360
I swear I won't bother you again.

93
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,970
I'll kowtow to you 18 times.

94
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,600
All right?

95
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:09,320
Mr. Wen was chased
by his enemies back then.

96
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:12,240
When my brother saved him,
he said this before.

97
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,680
He's alone

98
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,760
without relatives and friends.

99
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,760
So during this term's
Soul Combat Convention,

100
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:20,160
my brother strongly recommended him
as the examiner.

101
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,880
Make sure that there's no fraud

102
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,960
to silence everyone in the court.

103
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,340
How could you be his relative?

104
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,720
What you're saying is...

105
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,520
I can see him
in the Soul Combat Convention.

106
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:34,920
Cut the crap.

107
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,970
You must come with me today.

108
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:39,159
I'll investigate who the heck you are.

109
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,290
If you touch Lu Ping,

110
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,600
I'll kill them both.

111
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:42,760
Ziyan.

112
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,360
No wonder you're my godsister.

113
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:47,080
I have taught you well.

114
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,480
Sangsang.

115
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,730
I was sneak attacked
by this girl of Zhaifeng Institute.

116
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,840
Despicable.

117
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,200
Shameless.

118
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,240
Despicable?

119
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,940
If I was, would I exchange two for one?

120
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,320
Ms. Qin.

121
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,640
You got a better deal.

122
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,160
Let them go first.

123
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,840
Miss, your task is more important.

124
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,700
My life belongs to the Qin family.

125
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:15,440
It's not worthy of your troubles.

126
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,240
Don't move.

127
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,880
Miss.

128
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:25,040
Everyone's life belongs to themselves.

129
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:28,040
Even if you lose all your blood,
you should try to live.

130
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:30,170
How could you give up so easily?

131
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,799
Wasps!

132
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,520
Don't bite me!

133
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,280
Help!

134
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,640
Ziyan, save him.

135
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,560
Ms. Qin.

136
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:04,560
I'll see you when I see you.

137
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,970
Don't fall into my hands again.

138
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:10,960
Silly girl.

139
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,040
Ms. Qin.

140
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,040
Ms. Qin.

141
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,040
Where is she?

142
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:18,760
Zhao Xifan.

143
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,520
Lu Ping is the God of Bandits.

144
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,780
Ms. Qin knows about it.

145
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,220
She should be waiting for me here.

146
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,360
She must be nearby.

147
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,620
She can testify for me.

148
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:30,280
Enough, don't defame a disciple
of Zhaifeng Institute.

149
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,740
Let's go to the officials.

150
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,040
Could it be Lu Ping?

151
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,520
Today, I came here to capture a person.

152
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,720
But this place has someone highly skilled
sheltering them.

153
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:42,080
Since that someone is so kind,

154
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,280
he won't stand idly by.

155
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,440
Sorry for putting you guys through this.

156
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,240
Let's see how many lives are lost

157
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,880
before he shows up.

158
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,120
Where are you, Mr. Wei?

159
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,920
Mr. Zhao!

160
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,360
Save me quickly!

161
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,240
Zhao Xifan.

162
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,770
Do you know them?

163
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,880
My silver sickle remembers you.

164
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,360
Let's go.

165
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,320
Jump!

166
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,520
Sure enough, an arrow can kill.

167
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,800
You can't even hold a blade.

168
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:55,680
You're still as useless as before.

169
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:01,320
Take her.

170
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,400
Zhao Xifan.

171
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:04,920
Are you all right?

172
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:13,840
Lu Ping.

173
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,960
About your conversation with Ms. Qin,

174
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,040
I already heard it.

175
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,520
Xing Luo already reached Chenqiao Town.

176
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:21,000
Zhaifeng isn't safe anymore.

177
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,200
Maybe the Qins is a safe path.

178
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:25,880
Lu Ping.

179
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,280
The Qins can't win against Shanhai Gang.

180
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:32,340
Nobody can win against Shanhai Gang.

181
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,480
If Ms. Qin wants to die,

182
00:12:34,760 --> 00:12:35,600
it's up to her.

183
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,480
Anyway, we won't be captured again.

184
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,240
Zhao Xifan!

185
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,120
Wait for me!

186
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,600
You're heavily injured.

187
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,860
You'll bleed to death.

188
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:47,560
About Lu Ping.

189
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:49,410
You haven't figured it out yet.

190
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,560
You're not angry at him.

191
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,880
I still need him for the reward.

192
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:52,680
Shut up!

193
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:55,000
Even if Lu Ping's background is unclear,

194
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,840
he's still from Zhaifeng Institute.

195
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,040
You're the outsider.

196
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,650
Leave Zhaifeng Institute!

197
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,840
Hey.

198
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,720
Zhao Xifan.

199
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,280
Did you forget you were beaten

200
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:05,760
into a pulp in Ruyu Restaurant?

201
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,800
I'm your savior.

202
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,280
Go away.

203
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,520
Go away now!

204
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,720
I won't go away.

205
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:18,780
I'll walk away.

206
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:32,090
We can't stay for long
at Zhaifeng Institute.

207
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,960
Before Shanhai Gang finds us,

208
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:36,720
we must leave.

209
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:38,800
Leave?

210
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:39,960
Where to?

211
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,760
Soul Combat Convention.

212
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:44,120
But I need to pass the Chan State's exam

213
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,920
to qualify for the competition.

214
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:47,600
Didn't Master say

215
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:50,040
that for this year's
Soul Combat Convention,

216
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:52,000
the court will choose the contestants?

217
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,640
Lu Ping, do you want to be an official?

218
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:55,440
So during this term's
Soul Combat Convention,

219
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:57,680
Qin Qi strongly recommended him
as the examiner.

220
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,410
Make sure that there's no fraud

221
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:01,560
to silence everyone in the court.

222
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:05,560
The Qins are keeping their eyes
on Wen Gecheng.

223
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,760
The Qin family is rich and influential.

224
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:09,040
They won't simply accept people

225
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:11,040
with an unknown background like us.

226
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,160
Since Wen Gecheng

227
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:14,280
is the examiner of Soul Combat Convention,

228
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:16,210
this is our best chance to meet him.

229
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,920
Su Tang.

230
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:21,380
For the Chan State's exam,

231
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,680
I must win.

232
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:28,800
Please.

233
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,760
Sangsang.

234
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,280
The assassin is dead
while the other is injured.

235
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:36,600
Nothing will happen again.

236
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,520
You were startled.

237
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:39,000
Why don't you stay here for a few days?

238
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,280
Chan State's exam is near.

239
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:41,480
If I can get your guidance,

240
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,680
it's my honor.

241
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,600
Thank you for your kind offer, Mr. Wei.

242
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,860
If I stay in Chan State,

243
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:49,820
I'll cause many problems for you.

244
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,760
I already informed my brother to come

245
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,360
and bring me back to Kaifeng.

246
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,560
I won't bother you.

247
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:57,000
Have a safe journey, Ms. Qin.

248
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,860
Forgive me for not seeing you out.

249
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,120
Father.

250
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:10,360
Sangsang wants to leave.

251
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,160
Is it because

252
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:13,300
I was kidnapped by those two wild men?

253
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,620
It's so embarrassing.

254
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:24,040
[I'll remember you two.]

255
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:26,480
Miss.

256
00:15:26,800 --> 00:15:28,560
Are you really going back to Kaifeng?

257
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,760
Don't you want to stay for two more days?

258
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:31,920
Ziyan.

259
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,500
Have you thought about

260
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:36,080
why Xing Luo came to Ruyu Restaurant?

261
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:40,340
Although we lost the lead on Xing Luo,

262
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:42,960
but that bandit
from Shanhai Gang is right.

263
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:45,440
Our whereabouts are exposed.

264
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:48,260
Wei Tianqi rescued me before.

265
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:49,640
But when Wei family knows

266
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:51,600
that we're investigating Shanhai Gang,

267
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:53,240
they want to take credit for our work.

268
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:54,700
Acting on their own accord

269
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,200
is possible too.

270
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:00,500
Anyway, we should be careful.

271
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,680
Although that mister looks like a rogue,

272
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:06,680
he has a kind heart.

273
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,440
Miss, you still refuse to let him go.

274
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,160
I have a premonition.

275
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,040
As long as we can capture him,

276
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,680
we'll be one step from the truth

277
00:16:16,680 --> 00:16:17,610
of Shanhai Gang.

278
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,240
Also,

279
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:22,640
he's not a mister.

280
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:24,600
Suspicious whereabouts.

281
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,860
Despicable and nasty.

282
00:16:25,880 --> 00:16:27,040
He's a hooligan.

283
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:30,720
Without my permission,

284
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:32,340
