287
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,940
You're the Qin family's servant.

288
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,760
Your life isn't that worthless.

289
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,560
Yes, miss.

290
00:16:57,040 --> 00:16:57,840
Sir.

291
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,640
