293
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:05,599
One of the two messengers is already dead.

294
00:17:05,599 --> 00:17:07,319
Nothing must happen to the other person.

295
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:09,040
Something has already happened.

296
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,200
I followed your instructions

297
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,359
and made the arrangements.

298
00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:13,000
When I went to prison to pick her up,

299
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,400
Situ Luo killed a few disciples

300
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:15,260
and rushed out.

301
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:17,720
She's moving towards Chenqiao Town.

302
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:19,480
I already sent someone after her.

303
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:21,609
I'm not sure if they can make it on time.

304
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,400
You don't know how much my back hurts.

305
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,240
Me too.

306
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,160
Hello.

307
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:43,720
Rest early.

308
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:44,640
You guys too.

309
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,520
[A first-rate assassin]

310
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:04,920
