until reaches his last breath.]

311
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:06,560
[Lu Ping.]

312
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:10,000
[I have killed a person from Xing Luo.]

313
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:13,700
[I don't believe I can't handle you.]

314
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,840
Xing Luo?

315
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,160
Xing.

316
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:31,720
Your murderer is inside.

317
00:18:32,320 --> 00:18:34,960
Let's go have the fun of our lives now.

318
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:42,360
[Zhaifeng Institute]

319
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:56,720
I caused my good friend's death.

320
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:00,940
