323
00:19:10,840 --> 00:19:12,560
But you're still useless.

324
00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:14,400
[Save me.]

325
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:15,640
[Save me!]

326
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:17,280
[It's from Zhaifeng Institute.]

327
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:19,120
[Save me!]

328
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:23,320
Lu Ping!

329
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:25,800
What's wrong?

330
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,740
Situ Luo escaped from the prison.

331
00:19:27,800 --> 00:19:29,000
She went to Zhaifeng.

332
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:33,800
Let go of him.

333
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,040
Come at me instead.

334
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,360
Don't worry.

335
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:42,720
I won't let you guys die easily.

336
00:19:43,360 --> 00:19:44,880
After getting poisoned,

337
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:47,090
have a taste of a fate worse than death.

338
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,200
Don't blame me.

339
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,850
If you want to blame,

340
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,480
blame the person from Zhaifeng Institute

341
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:53,760
for killing my favorite slave.

342
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:55,920
Now,

343
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:59,000
tell your master to come out now.

344
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,560
Otherwise,

345
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:04,160
in the next moment, my silver sickle

346
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:08,560
will separate your head from your body.

347
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:11,400
Shut up!

348
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:12,280
Xifan.

349
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:13,240
You guys, shut up!

350
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:14,040
Xifan!

351
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:15,480
Shut up!

352
00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:21,680
Zhao Xifan.

353
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:22,680
Are you crazy?

354
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,800
Situ Luo came here to find us.

355
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,400
Do you want to go back and die?

356
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:28,400
Can't you hear their cries for help?

357
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,440
My ears are working.

358
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,570
My brain is fine too.

359
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:34,050
If you're smart, you'll choose to run.

360
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:36,240
If you're dead, how can you save them?

361
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:37,040
Let's go.

362
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:37,960
Follow me.

363
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:42,080
All right, you're a hero.

364
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:43,200
Tell me then.

365
00:20:43,360 --> 00:20:44,490
If you meet Situ Luo,

366
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:46,170
you can't even hold a blade.

367
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,840
Do you want me to try my luck again?

368
00:20:47,840 --> 00:20:48,720
Who knows if I could

369
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:50,180
get lucky the second time?

370
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:52,800
Leave then.

371
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:55,760
You don't belong to Zhaifeng Institute.

372
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:56,820
But I'm different.

373
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,400
I'm carrying this badge.

374
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:00,260
It means I'm the eldest disciple.

375
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:02,540
You won't understand.

376
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:07,840
He's crazy.

377
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,320
Everyone went crazy.

378
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:10,840
Xifan.

379
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:14,560
Save us.

380
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:15,920
Xifan.

381
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:17,600
Xifan.

382
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:18,480
Leave.

383
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:19,800
Xifan.

384
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:23,720
I was the mastermind

385
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:26,420
behind Ruyu Restaurant's incident.

386
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:29,200
Don't you want someone
to be buried with your slave?

387
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,320
Release the rest.

388
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,500
I'll bear it alone.

389
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:35,040
Xifan, leave us.

390
00:21:36,520 --> 00:21:38,000
Xifan, leave.

391
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:39,920
Xifan, leave!

392
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,120
Leave us!

393
00:21:41,360 --> 00:21:42,160
Leave.

394
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:43,840
You know you couldn't win against me.

395
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,640
But you still dare to come alone.

396
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:47,440
How interesting.

397
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:49,420
You guys made me lost my slave.

398
00:21:50,120 --> 00:21:51,200
Why don't

399
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:53,160
you become his replacement?

400
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,210
What do you want me to do?

401
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,240
It's easy.

402
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:01,320
You can save these people.

403
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:05,760
But I want you to use this silver sickle

404
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,520
and hook it on your shoulder.

405
00:22:07,600 --> 00:22:08,920
Just like a dog,

406
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:11,800
drag them out one by one.

407
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,880
The number of people you can save

408
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:17,400
depends on how tough your life is.

409
00:22:18,600 --> 00:22:19,440
Xifan.

410
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,200
Don't do it.

411
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:22,440
Xifan.

412
00:22:22,520 --> 00:22:23,320
Leave now.

413
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,560
Leave!

414
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,320
It's a deal.

415
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:32,400
Don't do it, Xifan.

416
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:33,200
Leave.

417
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:39,920
Xifan.

418
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:40,960
Xifan.

419
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:41,960
Stop it.

420
00:22:42,040 --> 00:22:43,040
Xifan.

421
00:22:47,280 --> 00:22:49,160
Xifan, leave us behind.

422
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:50,680
Leave us.

423
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:51,960
Xifan.

424
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:03,920
Xifan.

425
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,000
Stop it.

426
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:28,240
The assassin is here.

427
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,920
How could someone

428
00:23:40,080 --> 00:23:41,800
as sincere as you exist in this world?

429
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:42,600
Go away.

430
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:43,920
It's none of your business.

431
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,480
She's humiliating us.

432
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:46,760
If news of this spread out,

433
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:48,820
how can I be the world's top assassin?

434
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,330
I'll handle her.

435
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:56,400
This is the antidote.

436
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:57,600
Take it and save them.

437
00:24:28,560 --> 00:24:29,360
Su Tang.

438
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:32,480
I had the same nightmare for three years.

439
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:33,940
I finally understand now.

440
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:36,450
Escaping on every occasion...

441
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,820
will only implicate more people.

442
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:47,100
Xifan and that assassin
understand this point too.

443
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:49,600
Must you go?

444
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:51,760
Wait for me.

445
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:54,600
How touching.

446
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,730
One death isn't enough.

447
00:24:56,800 --> 00:24:58,000
He found a companion.

448
00:24:58,320 --> 00:24:59,440
Cut the crap.

449
00:25:19,120 --> 00:25:19,980
God of Bandits.

450
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,360
God of Bandits!

451
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,680
God of Bandits came to save us.

452
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:24,480
God of Bandits is here to save us.

453
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:29,240
Xifan.

454
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:30,200
How are you?

455
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:32,560
Save the others first.

456
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:36,100
I suffered so much.

457
00:25:36,280 --> 00:25:37,360
You finally came.

458
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:53,080
Get up.

459
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:54,480
Go.

460
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:55,440
Leave now.

461
00:25:55,520 --> 00:25:56,480
Leave!

462
00:25:58,800 --> 00:25:59,600
Mo Lin.

463
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:02,480
I killed a guy after all.

464
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:03,720
I don't believe

465
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,440
that I can't kill a lady.

466
00:26:25,360 --> 00:26:26,280
Mo Lin.

467
00:26:27,800 --> 00:26:29,520
Master hid a Flame Knife.

468
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:32,880
Use the soul of Pivot
and check where it was hidden.

469
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:41,060
It's below that calabash.

470
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,040
Su Tang.

471
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,140
We're counting on you.

472
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:57,240
Flame Rock.

473
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,800
[With Su Tang's soul of Strength,]

474
00:26:58,800 --> 00:27:00,400
[I hope we can ignite the Flame Knife]

475
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:01,530
[and stop Xing Luo.]

476
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:35,880
Lu Ping.

477
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:51,080
It's you.

478
00:27:53,760 --> 00:27:55,040
I must inform my lord.

479
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:05,760
Lu Ping.

480
00:28:07,520 --> 00:28:08,320
It's too late.

481
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:09,520
It's too late.

482
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:10,840
Capture Situ Luo back.

483
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:12,700
She can't return to Shanhai Gang.

484
00:28:26,760 --> 00:28:27,640
My hand hurts.

485
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:29,610
It hurts so much.

486
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:31,440
Who's that lady?

487
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,240
After I left,

488
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:34,450
did a thief enter Zhaifeng Institute?

489
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:40,650
What are you looking at?

490
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:43,440
I told you earlier on.

491
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:45,320
My martial arts is very amazing.

492
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:46,850
You witnessed it today.

493
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:49,960
Zhaifeng Institute surpasses Beidou.

494
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,360
The day will arrive soon.

495
00:28:59,320 --> 00:29:01,240
I was only gone for a few days.

496
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:05,170
You guys already almost destroyed
Zhaifeng Institute.

497
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:07,720
I'm old already.

498
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,720
In case I can't handle the news

499
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:10,960
and something happens,

500
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:12,400
can you guys bear the consequences?

501
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,200
Can you?

502
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:14,080
You...

503
00:29:15,320 --> 00:29:16,160
Lu Ping.

504
00:29:16,320 --> 00:29:17,520
It's definitely you.

505
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:18,800
It must be your fault.

506
00:29:19,040 --> 00:29:20,320
Tidy up Zhaifeng Institute's

507
00:29:20,320 --> 00:29:21,560
interior and exterior now.

508
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:23,560
If you can't finish, you can't rest!

509
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:25,600
-Go now.
-Hold it.

510
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,160
He can't leave.

511
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:32,080
Who's this?

512
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:33,520
I came here to capture him.

513
00:29:33,520 --> 00:29:34,780
-He's not...
-Master!

514
00:29:35,080 --> 00:29:36,920
This guy isn't a Zhaifeng's disciple.

515
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:38,440
Don't listen to his nonsense.

516
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:39,360
This...

517
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:41,880
I'm so confused now.

518
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:43,720
Zhao Xifan.

519
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,760
Don't you know everything about Lu Ping?

520
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:46,560
Tell him.

521
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:47,800
Master.

522
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,020
It was because of my careless action,

523
00:29:51,080 --> 00:29:52,140
I provoked an enemy

524
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:54,020
and implicated Zhaifeng.

525
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:55,840
Lu Ping fought to save the others.

526
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:57,040
Leave him out of this.

527
00:29:57,120 --> 00:29:58,240
I'm willing to bear

528
00:29:59,080 --> 00:30:00,360
the punishment alone.

529
00:30:03,280 --> 00:30:04,120
Zhao Xifan.

530
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:05,680
Who are you actually helping?

531
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,840
This guy is Mo Lin.

532
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:08,640
He trespassed Zhaifeng Institute.

533
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:11,170
Please hand him over to Su Tang
for detention.

534
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:12,840
If he speaks nonsense again,

535
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:15,600
please send him to the local authority.

536
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:16,960
You...

537
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:18,600
I beg you all.

538
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:20,200
Stop speaking nonsense.

539
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:22,240
Lu Ping.

540
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,000
Come with me.

541
00:30:27,080 --> 00:30:28,680
I have something to tell you.

542
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:37,540
Treat yourself first.

543
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:46,160
Lu Ping.

544
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:47,800
Hang on.

545
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:50,100
Take care of yourself before others.

546
00:31:07,040 --> 00:31:08,440
What actually happened?

547
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:20,610
Xifan is behaving oddly today.

548
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:22,610
Did he discover your identity?

549
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:33,970
We're about to part.

550
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:35,880
Why waste your time?

551
00:31:40,520 --> 00:31:41,520
Have you decided?

552
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:43,730
Are you really leaving?

553
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:46,640
Master.

554
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:49,540
For these three years,

555
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:52,600
thank you.

556
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,640
A debt must be repaid.

557
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:56,380
You don't have to thank me.

558
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:57,360
For these three years,

559
00:31:57,360 --> 00:31:59,360
you used that excuse to keep me here,

560
00:31:59,520 --> 00:32:00,850
so that I can feel at ease

561
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:01,760
and stay here.

562
00:32:02,040 --> 00:32:05,040
So that Zhaifeng Institute
can shelter me for a while.

563
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:07,340
But the chains bind me.

564
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:09,780
Shanhai Gang chases me day and night.

565
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:12,000
