who's more qualified.

658
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:35,500
Everything that has a beginning,
has an ending.

659
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:38,020
Even if you want to pass
this position to him,

660
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:39,810
