Go to the back of the mountain.

666
00:36:57,200 --> 00:36:58,000
Yes.

667
00:37:00,720 --> 00:37:01,520
Wait for me!

668
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:03,200
After I have the soul of Strength,

669
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:04,880
