Everyone is worried about you.

686
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:23,130
I never thought of saving them.

687
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,760
I fought because Xing Luo

688
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:29,080
threatened my safety.

689
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:31,160
Xifan.

690
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:33,340
Don't judge me by your standards.

691
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:36,000
We're different.

692
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:37,680
Lu Ping.

693
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:40,360
I just want to help.

694
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,800
You want to be a hero
who seeks justice for the weak.

695
